@doc """
Returns an `%Ecto.Changeset{}` for tracking ${1/(.*)/${1:/pascalcase}/} changes.

## Examples

    iex> change_$1(%{field: value})
    %Ecto.Changeset{data: %${1/(.*)/${1:/pascalcase}/}{}}

"""
def change_${1:name}(%${1/(.*)/${1:/pascalcase}/}{} = $1, attrs \\\\ %{} ) do
  ${1/(.*)/${1:/pascalcase}/}.changeset($1, attrs)
end
